<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Izdedim Seni kúnmen túnderde</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Izdedim Seni kúnmen túnderde,
 Jaıqalǵan sheksiz, alaý gúlderden!
 Izdedim Seni, taý men qyrattan,
 Syldyrlap aqqan, móldir bulaqtan!
 Jaratqan Iem, basymdy ıem,
 Jalǵanda, myna, Ózińdi súıem!
 Ómirim meniń, qolyńda Seniń,
 Keshirgen qansha, kúnámdy meniń!

[V2]
 Ótkizgen meni, ózen, kólderden,
 Saqtaǵan boran, ystyq shúlderden!
 Jetelep meni, jas balalarsha,
 Kútemin Seni, qaıta oralǵansha!
 Ózińe erem, janymdy berem,
 Qınalǵan shaqta, tek Saǵan senem!
 Ańsaǵan meniń, tańdarym ediń,
 Jubatqan meni, sózderiń, Seniń!
 Táńirim dedim, artamyn senim,
 Bárinen bıik, esimiń Seniń!</lyrics>
<author>Neızvesten</author>
</song>